      "writtenOn": "2020-07-06T21:48:09Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Do you feel strongly about this? Or would you be OK adding this later if we find this to be a problem?\n\nI\u0027m inclined towards leaving it as is in case we later switch to using Puppeteer\u0027s ElementHandle#type() method, which applies to any kind of element and not just inputs/selects.",
      "parentUuid": "3edeb72d_57f15adc",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 91,
        "startChar": 7,
        "endLine": 91,
        "endChar": 30
      },
      "revId": "924e7221b337648179b21b7f2e4b6e1dc350bba3",
