        "id": 5395
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-07-07T12:47:14Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The goal of the suggested name(s) is to make the upstack callers more skimmable. I would argue that Function.prototype.apply is not well-known enough where I consider it \"skimmable\".\n\nThus the suggestion for a set of very clear, explicit names. I\u0027m ok being redundant and extra  verbose to make these Page Objects more reader-friendly. Remember, this is test code, and test code should be written DAMPly so it\u0027s obvious it\u0027s correct, because tests don\u0027t have tests.\n\nIn a below comment, I enumerate a fresh set of names that I feel are nice and DAMP",
