      "message": "New name suggestions to account for this distinction\n\nexecuteOnPOE/executeOnPageObject\nexecuteOnAllPOEs/mapOverAllPOEs (or PageObject instead of POE)\nexecuteOnDOMElement\nexecuteOnAllDOMElements/mapOverAllDOMElements",
